<plot>Casa tells the story of a soldier's wife (Asia Agcaoili) who after learning that his husband (Michael Rovero) has gone "missing in action" rekindled an old flame (Paolo Paraiso). However, months later, her husband, who is temporarily blinded after doing combat in Mindanao, returns home. Because of his injury, he remains ignorant of the fact that he is sharing their casa ("house") with his wife's ex-lover.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?095593</url></doc>
